---
// StackTab.astro
---

<div class="tab-content" id="tab-stack">
      <div class="stack-page">

        <div class="stack-page-header">
          <div class="eyebrow" data-pl="Mapa stacku" data-en="Stack map" data-it="Mappa dello stack">Stack map</div>
          <h2 data-pl="Jak to buduję" data-en="How I build" data-it="Come costruisco">How I build</h2>
          <p data-pl="Kategorie technologii i jakie możliwości każda z nich otwiera." data-en="Technology categories I work with and what each one makes possible." data-it="Categorie tecnologiche e cosa ognuna di esse rende possibile.">Technology categories I work with and what each one makes possible.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="scat-list">

          <div class="scat-row">
            <div class="scat-name">Frontend</div>
            <div class="scat-icons">
              <div class="tech-icon-item"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/react/61DAFB" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'" alt="React"><span>React</span></div>
              <div class="tech-icon-item"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/typescript/3178C6" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'" alt="TypeScript"><span>TypeScript</span></div>
              <div class="tech-icon-item"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/tailwindcss/06B6D4" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'" alt="Tailwind"><span>Tailwind</span></div>
              <div class="tech-icon-item"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/vite/646CFF" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'" alt="Vite"><span>Vite</span></div>
              <div class="tech-icon-item"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/shadcnui/000000" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'" alt="shadcn/ui"><span>shadcn/ui</span></div>
              <div class="tech-icon-item"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/nextdotjs/000000" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'" alt="Next.js"><span>Next.js</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="scat-enables" data-pl="Buduję od landing page po pełne dashboardy SaaS - z type safety, server renderingiem i gotowym systemem komponentów." data-en="From landing pages to full SaaS dashboards - with type safety, server rendering, and a complete component system ready to extend." data-it="Da landing page a dashboard SaaS completi - con type safety, server rendering e un sistema di componenti pronto da estendere.">From landing pages to full SaaS dashboards - with type safety, server rendering, and a complete component system ready to extend.</div>
          </div>

          <div class="scat-row">
            <div class="scat-name">Backend &amp; Data</div>
            <div class="scat-icons">
              <div class="tech-icon-item"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/supabase/3ECF8E" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'" alt="Supabase"><span>Supabase</span></div>
              <div class="tech-icon-item"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/fastapi/009688" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'" alt="FastAPI"><span>FastAPI</span></div>
              <div class="tech-icon-item"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/googlecloud/4285F4" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'" alt="Cloud Run"><span>Cloud Run</span></div>
              <div class="tech-icon-item"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/googlebigquery/669DF6" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'" alt="BigQuery"><span>BigQuery</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="scat-enables" data-pl="Auth, baza danych i storage w kilka minut - potem własne API w Pythonie i BigQuery dla zapytań na milionach wierszy bez zarządzania serwerami." data-en="Auth, database, and storage in minutes - then custom Python APIs and BigQuery for querying millions of rows without managing servers." data-it="Auth, database e storage in pochi minuti - poi API Python custom e BigQuery per query su milioni di righe senza gestire server.">Auth, database, and storage in minutes - then custom Python APIs and BigQuery for querying millions of rows without managing servers.</div>
          </div>

          <div class="scat-row">
            <div class="scat-name">AI</div>
            <div class="scat-icons">
              <div class="tech-icon-item"><span class="tech-letter-mark" aria-hidden="true">AI</span><span>OpenAI</span></div>
              <div class="tech-icon-item"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/anthropic/D4A96A" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'" alt="Anthropic"><span>Anthropic</span></div>
              <div class="tech-icon-item"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/elevenlabs/F5A623" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'" alt="ElevenLabs"><span>ElevenLabs</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="scat-enables" data-pl="Dodaję generowanie tekstu, analizę dokumentów i głos do każdej aplikacji. Buduję agenty które rozumują, przeszukują i wykonują zadania automatycznie." data-en="Add text generation, document analysis, and voice to any app. Build agents that reason, search, and complete tasks without human input." data-it="Aggiungo generazione testo, analisi documenti e voce a qualsiasi app. Costruisco agenti che ragionano, cercano e completano task autonomamente.">Add text generation, document analysis, and voice to any app. Build agents that reason, search, and complete tasks without human input.</div>
          </div>

          <div class="scat-row">
            <div class="scat-name">Automation</div>
            <div class="scat-icons">
              <div class="tech-icon-item"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/zapier/FF4A00" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'" alt="Zapier"><span>Zapier</span></div>
              <div class="tech-icon-item"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/make/6D00CC" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'" alt="Make"><span>Make</span></div>
              <div class="tech-icon-item"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/n8n/EA4B71" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'" alt="n8n"><span>n8n</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="scat-enables" data-pl="Łączę systemy, które nie mają API. CRM, e-mail, webhooki, arkusze - gotowe w godziny, bez pisania kodu, bez sprintów." data-en="Connect tools that don't talk to each other. CRM, email, webhooks, spreadsheets - wired up in hours without writing a line of code." data-it="Collego strumenti che non comunicano tra loro. CRM, email, webhook, fogli - collegati in ore senza scrivere codice.">Connect tools that don't talk to each other. CRM, email, webhooks, spreadsheets - wired up in hours without writing a line of code.</div>
          </div>

          <div class="scat-row">
            <div class="scat-name">Payments &amp; Email</div>
            <div class="scat-icons">
              <div class="tech-icon-item"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/stripe/635BFF" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'" alt="Stripe"><span>Stripe</span></div>
              <div class="tech-icon-item"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/resend/000000" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'" alt="Resend"><span>Resend</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="scat-enables" data-pl="Subskrypcje i jednorazowe płatności z zarządzanym billingiem - plus maile transakcyjne, które trafiają do skrzynki, nie do spamu." data-en="Subscriptions and one-time payments with managed billing - plus transactional emails that land in the inbox, not spam." data-it="Abbonamenti e pagamenti singoli con billing gestito - più email transazionali che arrivano nella posta, non nello spam.">Subscriptions and one-time payments with managed billing - plus transactional emails that land in the inbox, not spam.</div>
          </div>

          <div class="scat-row">
            <div class="scat-name">Native / Desktop</div>
            <div class="scat-icons">
              <div class="tech-icon-item"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/swift/F05138" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'" alt="Swift"><span>Swift</span></div>
              <div class="tech-icon-item"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/apple/000000" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'" alt="AppKit"><span>AppKit</span></div>
              <div class="tech-icon-item"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/xcode/147EFB" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'" alt="Xcode"><span>Xcode</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="scat-enables" data-pl="Prawdziwe aplikacje macOS - nie wrappery Electron. Menu bar, system tray, local-first, pełny dostęp do API systemu, własny DMG." data-en="Real macOS apps - not Electron wrappers. Menu bar, system tray, local-first, full system API access, custom DMG distribution." data-it="Vere app macOS - non wrapper Electron. Menu bar, system tray, local-first, pieno accesso alle API di sistema, distribuzione DMG.">Real macOS apps - not Electron wrappers. Menu bar, system tray, local-first, full system API access, custom DMG distribution.</div>
          </div>

          <div class="scat-row">
            <div class="scat-name">Infrastructure</div>
            <div class="scat-icons">
              <div class="tech-icon-item"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/vercel/000000" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'" alt="Vercel"><span>Vercel</span></div>
              <div class="tech-icon-item"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/netlify/00C7B7" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'" alt="Netlify"><span>Netlify</span></div>
              <div class="tech-icon-item"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/cloudflare/F38020" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'" alt="Cloudflare"><span>Cloudflare</span></div>
              <div class="tech-icon-item"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/cloudflarepages/F38020" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'" alt="Cloudflare Pages"><span>Cloudflare Pages</span></div>
              <div class="tech-icon-item"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/github/181717" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'" alt="GitHub"><span>GitHub</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="scat-enables" data-pl="Push do gita = deploy gotowy. Vercel, Netlify i Cloudflare Pages dla edge hostingu, preview per branch, DNS i CDN bez ręcznego dłubania." data-en="Push to git, get a live URL. Vercel, Netlify, and Cloudflare Pages for edge hosting, branch previews, DNS, and CDN without manual glue." data-it="Push su git, URL live pronto. Vercel, Netlify e Cloudflare Pages per edge hosting, preview per branch, DNS e CDN senza configurazione manuale.">Push to git, get a live URL. Vercel, Netlify, and Cloudflare Pages for edge hosting, branch previews, DNS, and CDN without manual glue.</div>
          </div>

          <div class="scat-row">
            <div class="scat-name">Static &amp; Content</div>
            <div class="scat-icons">
              <div class="tech-icon-item"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/astro/FF5D01" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'" alt="Astro"><span>Astro</span></div>
              <div class="tech-icon-item"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/framer/0055FF" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'" alt="Framer"><span>Framer</span></div>
              <div class="tech-icon-item"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/webflow/4353FF" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'" alt="Webflow"><span>Webflow</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="scat-enables" data-pl="Ultraszybkie strony statyczne z Astro - 0kb JS domyślnie, idealne dla landing page, dokumentacji i content-heavy projektów gdzie liczy się Core Web Vitals." data-en="Ultra-fast static sites with Astro - 0kb JS by default, perfect for landing pages, docs, and content-heavy projects where Core Web Vitals matter." data-it="Siti statici ultra-veloci con Astro - 0kb JS di default, perfetti per landing page, documentazione e progetti content-heavy dove contano i Core Web Vitals.">Ultra-fast static sites with Astro - 0kb JS by default, perfect for landing pages, docs, and content-heavy projects where Core Web Vitals matter.</div>
          </div>

        </div>

      </div>
    </div><!-- /tab-stack -->
